  "body": "The issues, required to fix for onboarding flow (follow up on https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/15401)\r\n\r\n\r\n### ISSUE 1 Difference between design and actual implementation \r\n<img width=\"432\" alt=\"photo_2023-03-22 12 48 42 jpeg 2023-03-22 12-49-18\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/226896606-fc380b99-470e-4bf8-91da-6aab32479f2b.png\">\r\n\r\n- 6.1 The placeholder font color is not aligned\r\n- 6.2 The cursor color is not aligned\r\n- 6.3 No opacity either on IOS or on Android\r\n- 6.4 'Continue' button is overlapped by the keyboard and the view is not scrollable \r\n\r\n### ISSUE 2 Button continue is still available when validation is not passed\r\nTherefore, can create multi-account with invalid names.\r\n\r\n**Steps:**\r\n- set name with emoji \r\n- finish the flow\r\n",
